column5: So this report concludes my holidays for this time of the year. Looks like it's back to fishing 1 day a week or so until I'm off again at the end of July.  Total Hours Fishing - 2  Total Fish Landed - 4  Largest Fish - 16"      My brother in-law Andrew sporting the new waders I got him as a gift for graduating from U ot T. It's too bad he only caught 1 rock bass but he did hook into a huge smallie that took him into the branches of an overhanging tree. That was the end of that.     Hopefully another report to come by the end of next week.
That is a nice river Smallie Laszlo!  Bet it was a nice fight in the current.  Good fishin' and if you don't mind me asking, what do you like throwin at 'em?
Great report and pics laszlo Looks like you guys had a fun time out there!!! Thanks for sharing Leechman
